; Coverage for commodity.cc line 79: CURRENT_TIME() fallback in map_prices
; Without --now, the pricing code falls back to CURRENT_TIME()
; Verifies the conversion still works using the current time

P 2024/01/01 EUR $1.10

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses:Travel    500 EUR
    Assets:Checking

test bal --market --exchange '$' Expenses
             $550.00  Expenses:Travel
end test
